  section.slide#definition
    h2 Command Line Interface
    blockquote "a means of interacting with a computer program where the user (or client) issues commands to the program in the form of successive lines of text." - <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Command-line_interface">Wikipedia</a>

